&lt;p>This hole appears to be a core sample, taken by unknown persons. It&amp;rsquo;s not a drill mark, nor a tare and feather hole. Nor is it a rock worm, as suggested by some wags.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>To a non-expert, this rock seems to be sedimentary, then changed by heat into a metamorphic rock. Perhaps it is unusual and that&amp;rsquo;s why it was sampled?&lt;/p>
