data-flex-grow="133"
data-flex-basis="319px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>American Soldiers trained in this area when preparing for D-Day in 1945. Although hard to distinguish, the above feature was a former World War II Machine Gun Nest. Fortunately never needed on Dartmoor, but a sobering reminder of the many lives were lost across the Channel.&lt;/p>
